{
  "stem": "1917.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And so they started the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I began screaming and kicking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My number never came out clear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Four SS-- four-- two SS and two prisoners, women prisoners, had to restrain me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I said to myself, well, I need to find some kind of an excuse, because nice girls does-- do not do that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I said, I will cooperate with you if you bring my mother here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, they said, well, you could see her tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could think, really, how on earth will they reunite us tomorrow when they just stripped me apart from her earlier this morning?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- it seemed to be so-- such a bold lie that  I couldn't really accept it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- unfortunately, my poor sister believed it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She kept waiting for us to see my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She never told me about it until 1985.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They had a very tough time  with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I decided that I was not going to be a very cooperating victim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I kicked, screamed, and it's very difficult, because the way they do that number, they heated a pen like-- it looked like a writing   pen-- old-fashioned writing pen.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They heated it over open flame, then they dipped it into ink.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then dot by dot, they had to make out the letter A-7063.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, if you keep wiggling your arm, then is very difficult to make good number.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Merriam tells me that I bit the SS who was holding my arm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I still don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was a nice little girl, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't do something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
